  "original_title": "\u0d85\u0dbb\u0d9c\u0dbd \u0d9a\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dcf\u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dd2 \u0db4\u0dd0\u0dad\u0dd4\u0db8\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dbb\u0dca\u0db1\u0dbb\u0dca \u0d85\u0dad\u0dca\u0d85\u0da9\u0d82\u0d9c\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Struggle activist Pathum Karner arrested",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Colombo Crime Division says that one of the activists of the struggle, Pathum Kerner, who is said to have led the protest at Polduwa intersection in Battaramulla, was arrested today.",
        "Police say that he was summoned to Colombo Crime Division on the 18th, but he submitted a letter through a lawyer stating that he was suffering from illness.",
        "According to the police, Mr. Pathum Karanar has been staying near the Battaramulla Polduwa intersection, informing the people to come to the place through various means and leading the people there to break down the road barriers used for the security of the Parliament.",
        "There, two army soldiers who were among the security forces who tried to control the protestors were attacked and the militants also kidnapped the T-56 firearms and magazines containing live ammunition from them.",
        "The senior official added that a travel ban was also obtained from the court against Mr. Pathum Kerner, who is said to be a resident of Meeghawatta area."
      ],
